{
  "texts": [
    "One limitation of this study is the specific focus on text generation using GPT-4 Although GPT-4 is a widely utilized LLM, there are several other notable models offered by various companies, including (but not limited to) Google's Bard, GitHub's Copilot Chat, and Microsoft's Copilot (Agarwal, 2024).",
    "Furthermore, AI's capabilities extend beyond text to include the generation of visual outputs like graphs, figures, and charts, which are integral to APA writing.",
    "Consequently, this paper does not encompass the full breadth of generative AI or the spectrum of LLMs.",
    "Nonetheless, we believe that this study serves as a valuable starting point for exploring the use of AI.",
    "A final limitation is the inherent inability to replicate this study."
  ]
}